title: London/South Kensington-Chelsea
name: The Duke of York Square Shopping Complex
directions: Just off King's Road, near Sloane Square
image: https://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:Duke of York Square, SW3 - geograph.org.uk - 905597.jpg
content: Has a range of spacious branches of popular fashion chains, but lacks some of the road's character, however the small adjoining public space of Duke of York square is a welcome place for a rest between shopping, and a popular place to hang out.
